# PyTorch reference logits fixtures for P2.6 numerical correctness tests.
#
# Fixture files (`*.json`) in this directory are generated by running
# `tests/scripts/compare_logits_py_reference.py` in a Python venv with
# pinned torch/transformers versions. They are checked in so dotnet
# test can consume them without a Python dependency, but they are NOT
# regenerated automatically — each file lives for the lifetime of the
# pinned model weights + pinned torch/transformers combo.
#
# Regenerate a fixture when you bump the pinned transformers version,
# bump the model snapshot, or change dtype. See
# `RealHfSafetensorsEndToEndTests.Qwen25_0_5B_LogitsMatchPyTorchReference`
# for the consumer side and the Python script's docstring for the
# exact commands.
